    <string name="dialog_update_msg">After weeks of waiting, the CommonSense web interface is finally in a presentable state. Although it is still far from finished, you can have a peek at the collected data by logging in at http://common.sense-os.nl.\n\nWe recommend using a regular computer instead of your Android, because the interface is not really suited for smaller screens.\n\nHappy experimenting!</string>
